<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It'd be nice if I could configure a default route type so that I didn't have to specify type for each route when I'm using the same route type for dozens of routes.</p>

<p>API is simple:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$router-&gt;setDefaultRouteType('Zend_Controller_Router_Route_Regex');
</code></pre>

<p>Default would of course be Zend_Controller_Router_Route.</p>

